### CloudBees Genapp
This project contains the source for the CloudBees Genapp runtime, which is a private repository. If are interesting in developing ClickStack for CloudBees, please contact us at support@cloudbees.com and let us know your Github and CloudBees IDs and we can grant you access to this project.
